question: What is the population of Uppsala, Sweden as of December 31, 2020?
asked_question_translated: Koliko prebivalcev bo imelo mesto Uppsala na Švedskem 31. decembra 2020?
answer: Po ocenah je mesto Uppsala na Švedskem imelo približno 177.000 prebivalcev 31. decembra 2020.
answer_translated_eng: The city of Uppsala in Sweden is estimated to have a population of around 177,000 on 31 December 2020.
